{"tid":1992891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Be Water】流水式聚集 對抗限聚令","createTime":"2020-04-28T11:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T16:09:01.000Z","uid":60539,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d2bcbae8b5c409584178c01229ee1fa2859a5520","tid":1992891,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:48:44.000Z","msg":"面對港共刻意打壓<br />\n將限聚令延長至8月31日<br />\n而警方濫用兼選擇性執法<br />\n明眼人都知咩事<br />\n我建議係呢段期間<br />\n以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">流水式聚集</span></span>進行活動<br />\n所謂流水式聚集<br />\n即係唔會企定定等齊人<br />\n然後等人帶領<br />\n而係各自做自己野<br />\n但時機一到就同時一齊進行活動<br />\n<br />\n要做到呢樣野有三個步驟<br />\n1. 將手機時間set做由網絡供應商提供<br />\n<br />\n2.設定鬧鐘鈴聲為《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<br />\n歌可以直接係dgx巴打既網站下載<br />\n<a href=\"https://dgxmusic.com/glory-to-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdgxmusic.com%2Fglory-to-hk&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=21a708f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://dgxmusic.com/glory-to-hk</a><br />\n建議大家下載原版<br />\n<br />\nAn機可以直接set做鬧鐘鈴聲<br />\n而ios就麻煩啲<br />\n可參考<a href=\"https://www.mandyvincent.com/2019/09/Glory-to-hong-kong-ringtone-mp3-m4r-download.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mandyvincent.com%2F2019%2F09%2FGlory-to-hong-kong-ringtone-mp3-m4r-download.html%3Fm%3D1&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=dade4efb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mandyvincent.com/2019/09/Glory-to-hong-kong-ringtone-mp3-m4r-download.html?m=1</a><br />\n入面既教學<br />\n<br />\n3.將鬧鐘響鬧時間較做每次流水集合既指定時間<br />\n當歌聲響起眾人就合唱然後叫口號但同時保持流動<br />\n大家亦可以將snooze length set做5mins<br />\n即係5分鐘之後重新響鬧<br />\n又或者以此為開端然後進行其他行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住我地要Be Water!</span></span>"},{"pid":"f8e1251b729809be5d57dc641e7fff51efcf2874","tid":1992891,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:49:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Be Water!</span></span>"},{"pid":"337c07e3e849aa13db04643e58a2f5a9b157faa9","tid":1992891,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b728584662c3df719510d871778bcb2ba611c523","tid":1992891,"uid":60539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"如果成功更加可以發展到無孔不入<br />\n無固定地點<br />\n全港夠鐘一齊響起《願榮光》"},{"pid":"ceade6892a993b18a93ae893ed2f22a1499f3320","tid":1992891,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:52:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"51a7b7376ef7a0d6e95b731ee271987601f2e52e","tid":1992891,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:54:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a4730ab9daa601ec8be682783f8b0c6edda6e78b","tid":1992891,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be0596b616fd1ab24eeab115b930aa3970e4b92","tid":1992891,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"行動post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4e99c682edb663fdffc7ed85d8784d92056eed","tid":1992891,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:57:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b03fc5ad7038ef8776ea4f225722114c6fe58d","tid":1992891,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:58:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"746e09d5a97592bc2219932ad500b64978299fba","tid":1992891,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:58:40.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471fd45dfb412dfc8d4ff51ef8cf71cb8970cd2b","tid":1992891,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"